      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Lexus RX 350 in Deep Obsidian. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in impressive condition. The exterior retains a high-gloss shine, though there are minor, expected stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the driver\u2019s seat shows slight bolster creasing, but all power functions, the panoramic sunroof, and the premium audio system work perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound with a full service history at the local dealership. We recently completed a 60,000-mile service including a fresh oil change and brake inspection. The Michelin tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. This is a turnkey luxury SUV ready for its next owner. Includes two sets of keys and all original floor mats.",
